ince-1851-national-data-shows/0000018f-5d47-d0ec-a9cf-df5f2ce60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间以色列关系的场景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/scenes-from-an-israeli-relationship-during-a-war-in-gaza/0000018f-572c-d209-a79f-572d4fdb0000</link><description>当罗特姆·科迪什的伴侣从加沙服役回来后，她发现自己无法像以前一样与他交谈，所以她开始画插图来描述他们所经历的事情。这个每日系列记录了他们最私密的问题，强调了夫妻在战争时期如何应对</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 12:19:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/scenes-from-an-israeli-relationship-during-a-war-in-gaza/0000018f-572c-d209-a79f-572d4fdb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列，孤立吗？不要相信你读到的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-isolated-dont-believe-everything-you-read/0000018f-5d32-d9a0-a38f-fd371d080000</link><description>土耳其与以色列断绝贸易关系是新闻，但其他 120 个国家没有断绝贸易关系并不是新闻。铁的事实仍有待浮出水面，但以色列不应自满</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 12:00:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-isolated-dont-believe-everything-you-read/0000018f-5d32-d9a0-a38f-fd371d080000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡无视每一个警告。现在拜登告诉以色列：“够了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-every-warning-now-biden-is-telling-israel-enough-is-enough/0000018f-5cc6-d0ec-a9cf-dedf3a680000</link><description>由于大约 3,500 枚炸弹的运输目前已停止，美国总统乔·拜登向总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡发出关于在加沙开展地面行动的明确信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 11:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ignored-every-warning-now-biden-is-telling-israel-enough-is-enough/0000018f-5cc6-d0ec-a9cf-dedf3a680000</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，独立日前夕以色列人口达到 990 万</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-population-reaches-9-9-million-on-eve-of-independence-day-data-reveals/0000018f-5cd7-d9a0-a3